𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐀𝐤𝐢’𝐬 𝐃𝐚𝐲 🎉✨

We, the ITHM Student Council celebrates the 𝐒𝐭𝐮𝐝𝐞𝐧𝐭’𝐬 𝐖𝐞𝐥𝐟𝐚𝐫𝐞 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐆𝐫𝐢𝐞𝐯𝐚𝐧𝐜𝐞𝐬’ 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫—𝐌𝐱. 𝐀𝐧𝐠𝐞𝐥𝐢𝐤𝐚 𝐋𝐚𝐳𝐚𝐫𝐨.

We wish you another year filled with everlasting happiness, numerous opportuinities, continuos growth, and memories that can’t be beat!

Shine brighter Aki-star, we are so proud to have you with us! 🌟

Caption by: Marcus Arebuabo

𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐀𝐤𝐢’𝐬 𝐃𝐚𝐲 🎉✨

We, the ITHM Student Council celebrates the 𝐒𝐭𝐮𝐝𝐞𝐧𝐭’𝐬 𝐖𝐞𝐥𝐟𝐚𝐫𝐞 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐆𝐫𝐢𝐞𝐯𝐚𝐧𝐜𝐞𝐬’ 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫—𝐌𝐱. 𝐀𝐧𝐠𝐞𝐥𝐢𝐤𝐚 𝐋𝐚𝐳𝐚𝐫𝐨.

We wish you another year filled with everlasting happiness, numerous opportuinities, continuos growth, and memories that can’t be beat!

Shine brighter Aki-star, we are so proud to have you with us! 🌟

Caption by: Marcus Arebuabo

𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐀𝐤𝐢’𝐬 𝐃𝐚𝐲 🎉✨

We, the ITHM Student Council celebrates the 𝐒𝐭𝐮𝐝𝐞𝐧𝐭’𝐬 𝐖𝐞𝐥𝐟𝐚𝐫𝐞 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐆𝐫𝐢𝐞𝐯𝐚𝐧𝐜𝐞𝐬’ 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫—𝐌𝐱. 𝐀𝐧𝐠𝐞𝐥𝐢𝐤𝐚 𝐋𝐚𝐳𝐚𝐫𝐨.

We wish you another year filled with everlasting happiness, numerous opportuinities, continuos growth, and memories that can’t be beat!

Shine brighter Aki-star, we are so proud to have you with us! 🌟

Caption by: Marcus Arebuabo

#CultivatingLimitlessPotential 
#ITHMStudentCouncil

message.text:
𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐀𝐤𝐢’𝐬 𝐃𝐚𝐲 🎉✨

We, the ITHM Student Council celebrates the 𝐒𝐭𝐮𝐝𝐞𝐧𝐭’𝐬 𝐖𝐞𝐥𝐟𝐚𝐫𝐞 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐆𝐫𝐢𝐞𝐯𝐚𝐧𝐜𝐞𝐬’ 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫—𝐌𝐱. 𝐀𝐧𝐠𝐞𝐥𝐢𝐤𝐚 𝐋𝐚𝐳𝐚𝐫𝐨.

We wish you another year filled with everlasting happiness, numerous opportuinities, continuos growth, and memories that can’t be beat!

Shine brighter Aki-star, we are so proud to have you with us! 🌟

Caption by: Marcus Arebuabo

#CultivatingLimitlessPotential 
#ITHMStudentCouncil

message.text:
𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐀𝐤𝐢’𝐬 𝐃𝐚𝐲 🎉✨

We, the ITHM Student Council celebrates the 𝐒𝐭𝐮𝐝𝐞𝐧𝐭’𝐬 𝐖𝐞𝐥𝐟𝐚𝐫𝐞 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐆𝐫𝐢𝐞𝐯𝐚𝐧𝐜𝐞𝐬’ 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫—𝐌𝐱. 𝐀𝐧𝐠𝐞𝐥𝐢𝐤𝐚 𝐋𝐚𝐳𝐚𝐫𝐨.

We wish you another year filled with everlasting happiness, numerous opportuinities, continuos growth, and memories that can’t be beat!

Shine brighter Aki-star, we are so proud to have you with us! 🌟

Caption by: Marcus Arebuabo

#CultivatingLimitlessPotential 
#ITHMStudentCouncil
